parameters: \FF[yuri_smile]Yurika: "How's it going? Found out anything about the case?"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "So far... I'm still gathering information."

\F[beni_angry2]Akane: (Aside from the president, the suspects are Ayaka
Torii, Kikyo Seiryu, Shu Kamegami, Wata Shikura, Ama
Satsuki, and Kikuichi Washio. I need to talk to these six
first.)

\FF[yuri_smile]Yurika: "I see. Ah, that's fine. Ask me anything. I'm also
concerned about this incident."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "(She didn't refuse after all... I knew it, but... I
don't like this...)"

\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Thank you so much! It's really worrying, isn't
it? To think that such a pervert is lurking in our school."

\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "Among the teachers, there are indeed those rumored
to be appraising students with a lecherous eye."
\F[beni_true]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "Like Washio?"

\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Don't call a teacher by their name without
honorifics. But... he's definitely at the top of the list of
dangerous teachers, Washio-sensei."

\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[2]Yurika: "That's right. The student council has received many
consultations... or rather, complaints about him."

\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "It's not just Washio-sensei... We've picked up a
few suspects as the likely phantom. We'd like to know the
information the student council has on these people."

\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "As long as it doesn't involve privacy issues, it's
fine. Who do you want to hear about?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Before that, I have a question. Maintaining public
order is part of the student council's role, but isn't
searching for a criminal an overreach for the student
council?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "If we're not careful, we might lose the trust of the
teachers. I don't mind, but it could affect the president's
recommendations. Yet the president decided to cooperate with
us without any reward."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "That's what really bothers me."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "To bring up such a topic and then worry about it...
Hahaha... As expected of a detective."

\FF[nako_angry]Nadeshiko: "The student council president is willing to help
us! You're so stupid, Akane! I don't understand what you
mean!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[nako_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "But, but... maybe the president's intentions are
completely dark! Maybe she's planning to overthrow the
teachers and increase the power of the student council to
conquer the school..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[nako_angry]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "There's no way that's true! That's too rude,
Akane!"

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[nako_angry]\AA[1]Yurika: "No, Shiratora-san. It's only natural that no one
moves without benefit..."

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[nako_angry]\AA[1]Yurika: "It's understandable that Akane-san is concerned.
But... my reasons for benefiting are a bit complicated."
\F[beni_true]Akane: "Complicated...?"

\F[beni_true]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "It has to do with my upbringing. It's about how my
view on life made me this way."

\F[nako_true]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "The student council president's upbringing? I've
never heard about it..."

\F[nako_true]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "It's an embarrassing story. A laughable tale of an
awkward person. It's certainly not something I can boast
about."

\F[beni_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "When you were little, was your hobby doing ding-dong
ditch, and now you're making amends for it?"
\F[beni_smile]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "That's a terrible assumption..."
\F[beni_smile]\FF[yuri_laugh]\AA[2]Yurika: "Haha, you really are funny."

\F[beni_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "That's not it. When I was a child, I was a
worrywart. My parents were always troubled by me."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "It's hard to imagine from the current perfect
student council president who excels in both academics and
sports."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "That's what worried my parents. Since I was little,
I 'never relied on anyone.' I could do everything on my own
and never had any troubles."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Isn't that just bragging...?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "'From the time I was conscious, having a child who
could cook for themselves was understandably frightening.'

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[2]Yurika: "Moreover... apparently because I 'didn't need
others,' I became unable to take an interest in people."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Because you could do everything yourself... you
didn't need anyone... is that what you mean?"

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "A foolish child, right? But my parents advised me
this way, 'Be someone who is needed by others.'

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "'Fulfilling people's wishes' is what I need to be
with everyone."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "By being useful to others, I can feel that I'm
never alone. It's all thanks to my parents."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "So you're saying that cooperating just because
'you're needed' is enough...? Is that really okay?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Outlandish? But that's my benefit. So don't
hesitate. Feel free to ask me anything."

\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "I understand. But somehow, even the perfect
superhuman student council president has weaknesses. I feel
closer to you now."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "(No, not at all... This isn't a normal human
episode... It seems more like she's just bragging about her
own genius...)"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "('Fulfilling people's wishes'... If that's her
kink...? Then I still think the president is suspicious...)"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "So, will you tell me who the suspect... or rather,
who they are?"

\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Ye-yes! It's Torii-san, Seiryu-san, Kamegami-
san, Shikura-san, Satsuki-san, and Wao-sensei... those six
people!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "(She left out the president after all...)"

\FF[yuri_trouble]Yurika: "I once thought about inviting her to the student
council. But she declined, saying she wanted to prioritize
promises with friends."

\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Torii-san's brightness and friendliness really

\F[nako_smile]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "That's right. It's a shame... Nadeshiko-san, I also

\F[nako_shy]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Me...?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "That's right! Nadeshiko may seem this way but she's

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "There's no need to be modest. I properly recognize

\F[nako_shy]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Me... working under the president...? Is that
really okay? But I'm not confident..."

\F[nako_shy]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "I believe I have a good eye for people. You can do
it."

\F[nako_shy]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "(I've been praised... I'm needed by the
president...)"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko is an essential member of the Detective
Club! I wish you'd stop with the uncool recruiting..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "I understand. It just came up because we were
talking about Torii-san. But I'll always be waiting."
\F[beni_angry]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Grrrrr..."

\F[nako_shy]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "(Being wanted by both of them... My heart is
pounding... I'm troubled...)"
